	                                <p>&gt; And this is the second reason you might decide to map the inverse side of the relation:<br>it's required if you're doing a JOIN in this direction.</p><p>That's not true. As of Doctrine 2.3 or 2.4 (I don't remember anymore but both are already old anyway), arbitrary joins are supported, allowing to perform such joins without defining bidirectional relations.</p>
